<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="N" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Numb1" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Numb,</orth> adj. torpid, chill: <cit><quote>these feet, whose strengthless stay is n.</quote> <bibl n="shak. 1h6 2.5.13" default="NO" valid="yes">H6A II, 5, 13</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>the n. cold night,</quote> <bibl n="shak. r3 2.1.117" default="NO" valid="yes">R3 II, 1, 117</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>cold and n.</quote> <bibl n="shak. tit 3.1.259" default="NO" valid="yes">Tit. III, 1, 259</bibl></cit>.
